labels.label:
Restart api key quotas at the first execution of the day.
Check that api key quota is lower than 9200.

entry.value: BEGIN; WITH cte_quota AS ( SELECT api_key_quota FROM youtube_stats.api_key_quota WHERE api_key LIKE '${raw_channel_info_request:jsonPath('$.api_key')}' ) SELECT api_key_quota FROM cte_quota UNION ALL SELECT 0 AS api_key_quota FROM (SELECT 1) a LEFT JOIN cte_quota b ON FALSE WHERE NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM cte_quota)

entry.value: SELECT info.channel_id, CASE WHEN EXTRACT(HOUR FROM now()) > 6 THEN (now()::DATE - stats."timestamp"::DATE) ELSE ((now() - INTERVAL '1 days')::DATE - stats."timestamp"::DATE) END AS days_since_last_update, now() AS channel_timestamp FROM youtube_stats.channel_info info INNER JOIN youtube_stats.channel_stats stats USING (channel_id) WHERE channel_uri LIKE '${raw_channel_info_request:jsonPath('$.channel_uri')}' ORDER BY "timestamp" DESC LIMIT 1

entry.value: BEGIN; INSERT INTO youtube_stats.video_info (channel_id, video_uri, video_title, video_description, video_creation_date, video_duration, video_category, video_tags) VALUES ( ${channel_id}, '${raw_video_info_request:jsonPath('$.video_uri')}', '${raw_video_info_request:jsonPath('$.video_title'):replaceAll("\'","\'\'"):replaceAll("([;])","")}', '${raw_video_info_response:jsonPath('$.video_description'):isEmpty():ifElse('',${raw_video_info_response:jsonPath('$.video_description'):replaceAll("\'","\'\'"):replaceAll("([;])","")})}', '${raw_video_info_request:jsonPath('$.video_creation_date')}', 24*60*60*${raw_video_info_response:jsonPath('$.video_duration_days'):isEmpty():ifElse('0',${raw_video_info_response:jsonPath('$.video_duration_days')})} + 60*60*${raw_video_info_response:jsonPath('$.video_duration_hours'):isEmpty():ifElse('0',${raw_video_info_response:jsonPath('$.video_duration_hours')})} + 60*${raw_video_info_response:jsonPath('$.video_duration_minutes'):isEmpty():ifElse('0',${raw_video_info_response:jsonPath('$.video_duration_minutes')})} + ${raw_video_info_response:jsonPath('$.video_duration_seconds'):isEmpty():ifElse('0',${raw_video_info_response:jsonPath('$.video_duration_seconds')})}, ${raw_video_info_response:jsonPath('$.video_category')}, '${raw_video_info_response:jsonPath('$.video_tags'):isJson():ifElse(${raw_video_info_response:jsonPath('$.video_tags'):replaceAll("\'","\'\'"):replaceAll("([;])","")},'{}')}' ) ON CONFLICT (video_uri) DO UPDATE SET channel_id = EXCLUDED.channel_id, video_title = EXCLUDED.video_title, video_description = EXCLUDED.video_description, video_creation_date = EXCLUDED.video_creation_date, video_duration = EXCLUDED.video_duration, video_category = EXCLUDED.video_category, video_tags = EXCLUDED.video_tags ; SELECT video_id, now() AS video_timestamp FROM youtube_stats.video_info WHERE video_uri LIKE '${raw_video_info_request:jsonPath('$.video_uri')}' ; COMMIT;

entry.value: WITH fltr AS ( SELECT ARRAY ( SELECT '%' || fltr || '%' FROM JSON_ARRAY_ELEMENTS_TEXT('${raw_channel_info_request:jsonPath("$.filter_key_list")}') AS fltr(fltr) ) AS fltr ) SELECT * FROM youtube_stats.video_info vi, fltr WHERE vi.video_id = ${video_id} AND vi.video_duration >= ${raw_channel_info_request:jsonPath('$.duration_min'):isEmpty():ifElse('0',${raw_channel_info_request:jsonPath('$.duration_min')})} AND vi.video_duration <= ${raw_channel_info_request:jsonPath('$.duration_max'):isEmpty():ifElse('99999999',${raw_channel_info_request:jsonPath('$.duration_max')})} AND LOWER(vi.video_title) NOT LIKE ALL(fltr)

labels.label: One or more videos have experienced problems. TIme out of MergeContent triggered.
For each channel, it waits until all video stats are stored and then merges.
Process finished. Notify the next channel waiting.

entry.value: WITH count_video_stats AS ( SELECT COUNT(*) AS "count" FROM youtube_stats.video_stats vs INNER JOIN youtube_stats.video_info vi USING (video_id) WHERE "timestamp" > (now() - INTERVAL '5 minutes') AND vi.channel_id = ${channel_id} ) UPDATE youtube_stats.api_key_quota SET api_key_quota = api_key_quota + FLOOR(cte.count * ${raw_channel_info:isNull():ifElse('5.5','1.5')}) FROM count_video_stats cte WHERE api_key LIKE '${raw_channel_info_request:jsonPath('$.api_key')}'

INSERT INTO youtube_stats.video_stats (video_id, timestamp, view_count, like_count, favorite_count, comment_count) VALUES ( ${video_id}, '${video_timestamp}'::timestamptz, ${raw_video_stats_response:jsonPath('$.view_count'):isEmpty():ifElse('0',${raw_video_stats_response:jsonPath('$.view_count'):toNumber()})}, ${raw_video_stats_response:jsonPath('$.like_count'):isEmpty():ifElse('0',${raw_video_stats_response:jsonPath('$.like_count'):toNumber()})}, ${raw_video_stats_response:jsonPath('$.favorite_count'):isEmpty():ifElse('0',${raw_video_stats_response:jsonPath('$.favorite_count'):toNumber()})}, ${raw_video_stats_response:jsonPath('$.comment_count'):isEmpty():ifElse('0',${raw_video_stats_response:jsonPath('$.comment_count'):toNumber()})} ) ON CONFLICT (video_id, timestamp) DO UPDATE SET view_count = EXCLUDED.view_count, like_count = EXCLUDED.like_count, favorite_count = EXCLUDED.favorite_count, comment_count = EXCLUDED.comment_count
